name: The Jailbird From Prison With Love Club

metadata.name: TJFPWLC #1
metadata.description: The Jailbird From Prison With Love Club is a collection of 4'444 unique hand drawn Jailbird NFT's living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Jailbird doubles as your membership ID. By releasing a Jailbird from its cage you help the From Prison With Love Community (which includes real prison inmates) in their resocialisation journey. Visit www.oldpassion.ch for more information. Mainstream are many. We are unique. Just like you.
metadata.creator: oldpassion - from prison with love!
